source.name: Electric Generation By Fuel Type, GWh: Beginning 1960
source.description: New York Electric Generation By Fuel Type, GWh dataset provides data on total in-state generation for New York State. Sources of electricity include coal, natural gas, petroleum products, hydro, nuclear, waste, landfill gas, wood, wind, and net imports of electricity.
